    "body": "Ok, I think I know what you're observing.\r\n\r\nWhen you invoke `safeBatchTransferFrom`, if the arrays are contain a single element (in your example `[tokenId], [amount]`), the event that is emitted will be `TransferSingle` and not `TransferBatch`. This is why `expect(tx).to.emit(contractInstance, \"TransferBatch\")` is not finding an event.\r\n\r\nNote that this behavior is fully compliant with [ERC-1155](https://eips.ethereum.org/EIPS/eip-1155), so I will close the issue as resolved.",
